channel.title: How much would you pay?
channel.description:
Since I'm starting fresh and everything, I just thought I'd ask everyone how much they'd think I'd receive if I sold this account in RSGP? (RuneScape Gold Pieces). Fair enough its not the best of accounts but It's easy enough to earn cash.
Information; 1m worth of runes. 2-3m worth of seeds. 111 quest points. Random junk, etc.
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/10mmpty.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/n20q6u.png[/img]
Give me a honest opinion, I don't really care if its only worth 10m. I'd just like to know.
